data.description:
Welcome home to your adorable single-story home in the extremely popular Redbird Ranch! The yard boasts beautiful flowering trees, elegant landscaping, and a peach tree in the backyard. The extended back deck provides picturesque GREENBELT views amplified by an elegant wrought-iron gate fence. Watch the birds in the back yard while relaxing in your comfortable and upgraded open floor plan home. Abundant natural light, new wood-like vinyl flooring and high 9 ft. ceilings throughout will make you feel right at home. Enjoy ample storage exactly where you need it from the cabinet space and pantry in the kitchen to the partially floored attic and under-the-deck storage. The over-sized office features a custom built-in desk with shelving unit. Look forward to all the extras: Sprinkler system, gutters, custom lighting, security system and more. You're only a short walk from either neighborhood pool with splash park and playground (.5/.6m), or a quick drop-off at the high-rated NISD elementary right in the community, and middle school nearby. Plus enjoy the convenience of being minutes from all the shopping along both Potranco and Culebra Roads, and quick commutes to SeaWorld (20min), Lackland (17min), and NSA-Texas (20min)!
For a private showing, text MHNHomes to 59559.
